data.title: Jimmy Wales
data.meta_description: Jimmy Wales is Berkman emeritus and the founder and Chair of the Board of Trustees of the Wikimedia Foundation, a non-profit corporation that operates the Wikipedia project, and several other wiki projects.
data.text:
Jimmy Wales is Berkman emeritus and the founder and Chair of the Board of Trustees of the Wikimedia Foundation, a non-profit corporation that operates the Wikipedia project, and several other wiki projects.
